Explore these unusual images as scientists attempt to explain mysteries seen from space.Narrator: Steven KearneyS11 E1 - Secret Soviet SpacecraftS11 E2 - Range of Nazi EvilS11 E3 - Doomsday Lair of GreeceS11 E4 - Mystery of the Welsh MineS11 E5 - Riddle of Sardinia TowerS11 E6 - Circles of the High KingsS11 E7 - Russia's Lightning LabS11 E8 - Poland's Secret Nazi CompoundS11 E9 - Holes of Dead Sea DestructionS11 E10 - Ancient Rome's El Dorado
